        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "A new options should be added for all adapters where the language can be determinated.\n\n\"scanDirectory\"... should scan and add all source files within the given directory.\nAdapters like \"TMX\" can integrate it automatically.\n\nOther adapters like \"Gettext\" or \"CSV\" have to be named with a defined schema to be automatically recognised.\n\nEigther the file is named \"locale\".mo....\nor the file is named like Myfile.\"locale\".mo...\nor the file is named like Myfile_\"locale\".mo...\nor the file is named like Myfile-\"locale\".mo"
